{"tid":280611,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"尋漫畫","createTime":"2017-06-12T08:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T14:48:11.000Z","uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68e8a044ca828d2857663e82ecf2866baf5acccb","tid":280611,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"話說之前睇過一本漫畫,當時應該剛剛出,所以得幾話,<br />\n但覺得幾好笑,可惜唔記得叫咩名,<br />\n呢幾日醒起本野,想搵返黎睇,<br />\n內容大概係講個男主角被選為勇者,<br />\n之後有個新手導師既野帶佢打怪,<br />\n之後遇到隻巨大史萊姆,<br />\n之後就好簡約咁對打,新手導師叫佢殺咗佢<br />\n最後隻史萊姆好慘咁打電話返屋企留遺言同家人道別,<br />\n男主角又話「點殺得落手呀」咁上下既野,<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲們睇過呢套野知詭叫咩?<br />\n<br />\n再搭單問多本,<br />\n本野係講中二病會變成現實,<br />\n即個人患有中二病真係變成有佢幻想嗰種力量,<br />\n有個人就負責對付呢班人,佢好似會召喚啲人出黎對抗咁"},{"pid":"84ac578174787ea1affed8e3b90188055521a030","tid":280611,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"有無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666a34147b42e2e38ab696c715bdf1fe38ac794d","tid":280611,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"真係無人知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55115861a453fbbfe651d89169d0840750a101ec","tid":280611,"uid":82028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"我唔知"},{"pid":"2e4be141f64e28969c2ca3d58c8ff5ecc50f2b9f","tid":280611,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"2係至高指令?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277da6ed5310aefa7ce3d1c4a916f16562770bb8","tid":280611,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2係至高指令?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係啦應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p